    "name": "Hex Bots",
    "steam_appid": 3230330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are hunted by a rogue computer program. Avoid the bot either by yourself or cooperate with others while attempting to collect electrical components around the world to activate beacons to open the escape hatch.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hex Bots is a horror chaser game where you can play alone or with up to 3 other players. Your goal is to pick up electrical components in order to connect circuits on the computers scattered around the map, all while avoiding the demonic rogue artificial intelligence called Ounce.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hex Bots is best enjoyed as an online party game. There are various objectives, some that advances direct progression, and others that give you permanent boosts, and the players decide who will work on what. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/cf60e8f29b2b88f3a08a4468de4796bc.poster.avif?t=1746016589\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/cf60e8f29b2b88f3a08a4468de4796bc.webm?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/cf60e8f29b2b88f3a08a4468de4796bc.mp4?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frantically collect components in order to activate PCs around the map by completing a circuit connecting mini game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/a3bb82f19ad84e2970f3afff4231cf18.poster.avif?t=1746016589\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/a3bb82f19ad84e2970f3afff4231cf18.webm?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/a3bb82f19ad84e2970f3afff4231cf18.mp4?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/dc9ffd503ffcea02734fafae9be9dd53.poster.avif?t=1746016589\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/dc9ffd503ffcea02734fafae9be9dd53.webm?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/dc9ffd503ffcea02734fafae9be9dd53.mp4?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the feeling of wandering through a forgotten and unfinished world. Nothing is as it seems here. A liminal space with no cohesion or rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/926279432f6be873dccebce9e9e7b17e.poster.avif?t=1746016589\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/926279432f6be873dccebce9e9e7b17e.webm?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/926279432f6be873dccebce9e9e7b17e.mp4?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/73fb6d05d779bbb1c1d356d29b44e56e.poster.avif?t=1746016589\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/73fb6d05d779bbb1c1d356d29b44e56e.webm?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/73fb6d05d779bbb1c1d356d29b44e56e.mp4?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Got friends? The game will get no easier as the the rogue program will dynamically adapt to how many people you play with. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/dd66dd1c4fbf4a1c637cbda6e5c34ddd.poster.avif?t=1746016589\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/dd66dd1c4fbf4a1c637cbda6e5c34ddd.webm?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/dd66dd1c4fbf4a1c637cbda6e5c34ddd.mp4?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/f658aac9f7ed763c0614d5f1187db48d.poster.avif?t=1746016589\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/f658aac9f7ed763c0614d5f1187db48d.webm?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230330/extras/f658aac9f7ed763c0614d5f1187db48d.mp4?t=1746016589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're not entirely without tricks. Discover different side objectives in order to gain certain advantages to help you succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
